              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "A 2.6 mg/cm**2 thick self-supporting Cu-65 foil,",
                "isotopically enriched to 99.7%, was used as target."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "TELES",
                "SI",
                "COMPL",
                "SCIN"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The detector system was consisted",
                "of an annular Si telescope, the EXOGAM gamma array with",
                "11 Compton-suppressed clovers and a neutron array of 45",
                "liquid scintillator elements.Charged particles were",
                "detected in annular Si telescopes comprising delta-E,",
                "approx. 50 mum and E-detector, approx. 500 mum.",
                "The angular resolution was approx. 1.7 degree. The",
                "energy resolution for elastically scattered particles",
                "was approx. 300 keV."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "*By authors*.Absolute cross sections were obtained from",
                "the known efficiencies, target thickness and integrated",
                "beam intensity."
              ]
            }
